snippet.title: Star Wars Battlefront Rogue One: Scarif - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Star Wars™ Battlefront™ Rogue One: Scarif has new and exciting content inspired by Rogue One™: A Star Wars™ Story. 

Battle across four new maps on the tropical planet of Scarif. Play as two new heroes Jyn Erso and Orson Krennic, and blast opponents in a brand new multi-stage game mode with new weapons and Star Cards. 

Season Pass Owners, play Rogue One: Scarif on December 6.
